def recovery(C, F, T):
    if F * (C - T) == 0:
        return 0
    else:
        return C * (F - T) / F / (C - T) * 100

df_train['final.output.recovery_calculated'] = df_train.apply(lambda x: recovery(x['final.output.concentrate_au'], x['rougher.input.feed_au'], x['final.output.tail_au']), axis=1)
df_train['rougher.output.recovery_calculated'] = df_train.apply(lambda x: recovery(x['rougher.output.concentrate_au'], x['rougher.input.feed_au'], x['rougher.output.tail_au']), axis=1)
mae_final = mean_absolute_error(df_train['final.output.recovery'], df_train['final.output.recovery_calculated'])
mae_rougher = mean_absolute_error(df_train['rougher.output.recovery'], df_train['rougher.output.recovery_calculated'])

sMAPE sMAPE_w. sMAPE_w .

In [44]:
def sMAPE(target, predicted):
    return (abs(target - predicted) / (target + predicted) * 2).sum() / len(predicted) * 100

def sMAPE_w(target, predicted):
    target = pd.DataFrame(target).reset_index(drop=True)
    predicted = pd.DataFrame(predicted)
    predicted.columns = target.columns
    sums = target + predicted
    sums = sums.where(sums != 0, 1) 
    smapes = (2 * abs(target - predicted) / sums).sum() / sums.shape[0] * 100
    return 0.25 * smapes[0] + 0.75 * smapes[1]

scorer_wsMAPE = make_scorer(sMAPE_w, greater_is_better=False)
